lex: memory leak, event listener, cleanup, resource leak, unsubscribe, DOM cleanup, garbage collection, event handler, memory management  
vec: A script that detects and removes unused event listeners to prevent memory leaks in JavaScript applications  
hyde: function cleanupEventListeners() { document.removeEventListener('click', handleEvent); }

